[SN]TITLE[SN]
Grenade found on A483 roadside near Wrexham

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An old grenade has been found at the side of a road near Wrexham, North Wales Police has said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Traffic officers attended the A483 near junction 7 for Rossett after the device was found just before midday.
Army experts were sent to the scene to remove the grenade.
Police said the road had not been closed.
